// Windows resource script — embeds AUDIO.ico in the PE header so the
// .exe shows the correct icon in Explorer / taskbar / Alt-Tab without
// any runtime work. The runtime glfwSetWindowIcon() call covers the
// titlebar on platforms where rc-bound icons aren't visible.
//
// IDI_ICON1 = first icon resource; Windows shells pick the lowest-numbered
// icon for shortcuts. AUDIO.ico lives at the repo root, two levels up
// from this .rc file.
IDI_ICON1 ICON "../../AUDIO.ico"
